msgid "Hybrid Thinking Models"
msgstr "混合思考模型"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:157
msgid ""
"Some LLMs are marked as ``hybrid`` and can run with or without thinking "
"mode."
msgstr "部分大型語言模型標記為 ``混合型`` ，可選擇是否啟用思考模式運行。"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:159
msgid "Request-level ``enable_thinking`` is added in v1.17.0"
msgstr "請求層級的 ``enable_thinking`` 開關在 v1.17.0 支援"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/chat.rst:162
msgid ""
"Xinference exposes a request-level ``enable_thinking`` switch that works "
"across different model templates (e.g. Qwen uses ``enable_thinking`` while "
"some DeepSeek templates use ``thinking``)."
msgstr ""
"Xinference提供請求級別的 ``enable_thinking`` 開關，該開關適用於不同模型模板（例如Qwen使用 "
"``enable_thinking`` ，而部分DeepSeek模板使用 ``thinking`` ）。"

